TI  - beSEL: A Human-Aligned LLM Teaching Assistant for Enhancing Social-Emotional Learning
AU  - Zhang, Jing
AU  - Niu, Yazhe
AU  - Li, Xueyan
AU  - Zhou, Peiyan
AU  - Sun, Di
