TI  - YMCQ: Reasoning-Enhanced MCQ Generation
AU  - Dutulescu, Andreea
AU  - Ruseti, Stefan
AU  - Iorga, Denis
AU  - Dascalu, Mihai
AU  - McNamara, Danielle S.
T2  - 26th International Conference on Artificial Intelligence in Education-AIED
A2  - Cristea, A. I.
