TI  - Building Intelligent Educational Agents: A Scalable LLM-Based Framework for Assessment Generation
AU  - Gahar, R.M.
AU  - Gorchene, B.
AU  - Hidri, A.
AU  - Arfaoui, O.
AU  - Hidri, M.S.
